name: strangelove
description: It's been 4 years and I still can't decide if I'm in love or just on a maniac phase. This ain't about the picture itself, but our history. I met this girl called Lola about 7 years ago. We found each other again some years latter, a whole lot of shit happened, except for us being really together. I instantly sent her this pic when passing by this bar. Today, once again, I question myself about my own feelings. This is a simple and personal piece, I just wanna have it registered somehow.
